channel.title: Deeper Sounds of Nairobi
channel.description: Deeper Sounds of Nairobi is a dose of House music.Featuring guest DJs, Artists and Producers from Africa. Deeper Sounds of Nairobi is a promotional radio show recorded and produced in various corners of the world. These two shows are committed to showcasing musical talent coming out of Africa in the House/Dance Genre.

item.title: Deeper Sounds Of Nairobi #048 - Ibiza, Spain
item.description:
Ibiza Sunset mix coming to you live from the beautiful San Antonio Bay in Ibiza. Special thanks to Nereida for the Artist Residency collaboration this past Summer. Looking forward to many More!
VIDEO of DJ Set - https://t.co/MiYcPUQE4Q
Aparthotel Nereida is situated on San Antonio Bay beside the sea, on a rocky beach, 300 metres from the sandy beach Cala Xinxo and 1,200 metres from Port des Torrent , come experience the wonderful sunsets that this amazing venue has to offer.
